author: Stephen Sorace
title: Florida police, veterans group send off fallen vet as coronavirus puts military honors on hold
description: A Florida police department and veterans group stepped up to honor a veteran and retired police officer who died last week as the coronavirus pandemic has put military funeral honors on hold.
